## 🗺️ Monolithic Architecture Blueprint

This ecosystem operates as a classic full-stack monolith inside an isolated, private Docker bridge network (`wisgeek-network`). Because the JSP view layer is processed directly by the embedded web container (Tomcat) alongside your Spring controllers, front-end actions and back-end events execute within the same container context.

```text
               ┌───────────────────────────┐
               │    User Browser / Client  │
               └─────────────┬─────────────┘
                             │
       ┌─────────────────────┼─────────────────────┐
       ▼ (Port 8040)         ▼ (Port 8081)         ▼ (Port 3000)
┌──────────────────────┐┌──────────────┐      ┌──────────────┐
│  Full-Stack Monolith ││   Adminer    │      │ Grafana GUI  │
│  [JSP Views + MVC]   ││ (Database UI)│      │ (Visuals/UI) │
└──────────┬───────────┘└──────┬───────┘      └──────▲───────┘
           │                   │                     │
           │ (Internal:5432)   │ (Internal:5432)     │ (Internal:3100)
           ▼                   ▼                     │
┌──────────────────────────────────────┐             │
│         PostgreSQL Database          │             │
│     (Volume-persistent Storage)      │             │
└──────────────────────────────────────┘             │
           │                                         │
           │ (Standard Out Logs Shared)              │
           ▼                                         │
┌────────────────────┐ Push Logs (Internal:3100) ┌───┴──────────┐
│      Promtail      ├──────────────────────────►│ Grafana Loki │
│ (Log Stream Agent) │                           │ (Aggregator) │
└────────────────────┘                           └--------------┘

```

